â“ Question: What types of integration patterns are supported in SAP CPI?
ğŸ’¬ Answer: SAP CPI supports several integration patterns such as ğŸ“¤ Message Mapping, ğŸš¦
Data Routing, ğŸ“¦ Content-Based Routing, ğŸ¤– Orchestration, and ğŸ“¢ Publish-Subscribe.
These integration patterns help design different types of integration flows based on business requirements.
